               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_153" n="N022"/><rs type="person" key="Flew, A.">Flew, A.</rs> and <rs type="person" key="MacIntyre, ">MacIntyre</rs>--*New Essays in Philosophical Theology (Ch. I, VI, VII)
